          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Transform your bathroom with Otti Australia’s luxurious and thoughtfully crafted basins, baths, and LED mirrors. Known for their seamless blend of form and function, Otti fixtures offer premium quality and timeless design for modern Australian homes.</strong></p>"
          }
        }
      },
