      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_ijwtc4": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Otti Baths – Luxury and Comfort for Your Relaxation Space",
            "heading_size": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text_7Ncpcd": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Indulge in luxury with Otti Australia's selection of baths. Designed to provide a relaxing and rejuvenating experience, our baths are the perfect centrepiece for any bathroom. Otti baths offer a relaxing and rejuvenating experience, serving as the centerpiece of any luxury bathroom. The <a href=\"URL\">Otti Attica Noosa Bath Gloss White 1700mm</a> combines elegance and comfort, perfect for creating a personal sanctuary in any bathroom.</p><p><strong>Spacious Designs:</strong> Deep and spacious to offer maximum comfort.</p><p><strong>Elegant Lines: </strong>Modern aesthetics that enhance your bathroom's appeal.</p><p><strong>High-Quality Materials: </strong>Built to withstand daily use while maintaining their beauty.</p><p>Browse our range of Otti baths to create your personal sanctuary.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
        "button_baNGGT": {
          "type": "button",
