    "rich_text_YAPk9x": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "text_r86gW9": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3>What makes Otti Australia bathroom fixtures unique compared to other brands?</h3>"
          }
        },
        "text_pEhfwW": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Otti Australia is dedicated to creating bathroom fixtures that combine aesthetic design, premium materials, and innovative features. Each product is crafted with meticulous attention to detail and functionality, ensuring both durability and elegance. Whether you’re looking for basins, baths, or LED mirrors, Otti fixtures add a luxurious touch to any bathroom space while meeting rigorous quality standards.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "text_r86gW9",
        "text_pEhfwW"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "desktop_content_position": "center",
        "content_alignment": "left",
        "color_scheme": "background-1",
        "full_width": true,
        "padding_top": 0,
        "padding_bottom": 20
      }
    },
    "rich_text_yRFtnF": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "text_dzJL9c": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3>Are Otti basins easy to clean and maintain?</h3>"
          }
        },
        "text_nYw4Cj": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Yes, Otti basins are designed to be low-maintenance and easy to clean. The materials used are resistant to staining, scratches, and other forms of wear, ensuring that they maintain their appearance over time. For best results, use a mild, non-abrasive cleaner and avoid harsh chemicals to preserve the finish and integrity of the basin.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "text_dzJL9c",
        "text_nYw4Cj"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "desktop_content_position": "center",
        "content_alignment": "left",
        "color_scheme": "background-1",
        "full_width": true,
        "padding_top": 0,
        "padding_bottom": 20
      }
    },
    "rich_text_hYmdKi": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "text_Gf3PXg": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3>Are Otti basins available in different finishes?</h3>"
          }
        },
        "text_LQqwwB": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Yes, Otti basins come in a variety of finishes, allowing you to select the one that best complements your bathroom decor. Common finishes include matte, gloss, and textured surfaces for a unique aesthetic.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "text_Gf3PXg",
        "text_LQqwwB"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "desktop_content_position": "center",
        "content_alignment": "left",
        "color_scheme": "background-1",
        "full_width": true,
        "padding_top": 0,
        "padding_bottom": 20
      }
    },
    "rich_text_axy7Gc": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "text_4jCxxt": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3>Can Otti bathroom fixtures fit into a modern, minimalist design?</h3>"
          }
        },
        "text_MXk9t7": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Absolutely. Otti Australia offers a variety of minimalist-inspired designs that are perfect for contemporary bathrooms. Their basins, baths, and mirrors feature clean lines, neutral finishes, and streamlined shapes that enhance a modern aesthetic without overpowering the space. These fixtures are versatile and can fit into various bathroom designs, from minimalist to more eclectic styles.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "text_4jCxxt",
        "text_MXk9t7"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "desktop_content_position": "center",
        "content_alignment": "left",
        "color_scheme": "background-1",
        "full_width": true,
        "padding_top": 0,
        "padding_bottom": 20
      }
    },
    "rich_text_eEn9rT": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "text_eVn3J9": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3>What are the benefits of LED mirrors?</h3>"
          }
        },
        "text_DGk4U3": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Otti’s LED mirrors offer enhanced lighting for optimal visibility, ideal for grooming and makeup application. They often include anti-fog features, ensuring a clear reflection even in steamy conditions, adding both functionality and style to your bathroom.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "text_eVn3J9",
        "text_DGk4U3"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "desktop_content_position": "center",
        "content_alignment": "left",
        "color_scheme": "background-1",
        "full_width": true,
        "padding_top": 0,
        "padding_bottom": 20
      }
    },
    "rich_text_qnqpef": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "text_nyY7xr": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3>What are the installation requirements for Otti baths and basins?</h3>"
          }
        },
        "text_hxFJYN": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Otti recommends professional installation for its baths and basins to ensure proper setup and compliance with warranty conditions. Basins often require secure mounting and sealing, while baths may need plumbing adjustments and a stable base. Professional installation guarantees that each fixture is fitted correctly, preventing potential issues down the line and ensuring a seamless look in your bathroom.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "text_nyY7xr",
        "text_hxFJYN"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "desktop_content_position": "center",
        "content_alignment": "left",
        "color_scheme": "background-1",
        "full_width": true,
        "padding_top": 0,
        "padding_bottom": 20
      }
    },
    "rich_text_Cb37qB": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "text_bwqUEk": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3>What types of baths does Otti offer, and how do I select the right one for my bathroom?</h3>"
          }
        },
        "text_i9d8ke": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Otti Australia offers a variety of bath types, including freestanding, back-to-wall, and inset baths, allowing flexibility in design and space usage. When choosing a bath, consider the size of your bathroom, the type of bathing experience you desire (e.g., deep soak vs. quick rinse), and the aesthetic you want to achieve. Freestanding baths make a statement in larger bathrooms, while back-to-wall baths can save space in more compact layouts.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "text_bwqUEk",
        "text_i9d8ke"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "desktop_content_position": "center",
        "content_alignment": "left",
        "color_scheme": "background-1",
        "full_width": true,
        "padding_top": 0,
        "padding_bottom": 20
      }
    },
    "rich_text_cyGJR9": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "text_7LNcKQ": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3>Are Otti products covered by a warranty?</h3>"
          }
        },
        "text_iVNW6x": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Yes, Otti Australia offers warranties on their products to ensure quality and customer satisfaction. The specific warranty period may vary by product, so it's recommended to check the product details or contact customer support for more information.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "text_7LNcKQ",
        "text_iVNW6x"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "desktop_content_position": "center",
        "content_alignment": "left",
        "color_scheme": "background-1",
        "full_width": true,
        "padding_top": 0,
        "padding_bottom": 20
      }
    },
    "rich_text_AiE6zx": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "text_YxzGgP": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3>Can I install Otti bathroom fixtures myself?</h3>"
          }
        },
        "text_pdLVpU": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>While some fixtures can be installed by experienced DIY enthusiasts, we recommend professional installation for optimal results and to maintain warranty coverage, especially for complex installations like baths and basins.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "text_YxzGgP",
        "text_pdLVpU"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "desktop_content_position": "center",
        "content_alignment": "left",
        "color_scheme": "background-1",
        "full_width": true,
        "padding_top": 0,
